Rlease check-list 
-----------------

* Fix copyright header in all the files.

* `defaultconfig` under tayra/__init__.py must be consistent with
  docs/config.etx document. Must also be consistent with pluggdapps-bootstrap
  definition of tayra config parameters.
* Change the release version in 
    ./CHANGELOG,
    ./tayra/__init__.py
* Update setup.py and MANIFEST.in for release
* Create a tag and push the tagged branch to code.google.com
* Upload the source into pypi.
        make upload
